tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣可以脫離realism mode?<br />\n大家建唔建議咁做?</blockquote><br />\nadd me ,flightkingdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2cd94b06d74546de47e80b7013f6cac3753fcf","tid":120370,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3fed18c295076ba5367172f6c695df8279423931","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pish</blockquote><br />\n估唔到有香港人玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我新手剛剛加入多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50a1e19385aa344b5311818ba87bb6f0c88a700","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pish</blockquote><br />\n估唔到有香港人玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我新手剛剛加入多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前AM1 個陣高登好多人玩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0c8a30032bacb80a9d59af2a1c5dc2c7ed11cf","tid":120370,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:50:49.000Z","msg":"點決定買二手機<br />\n同埋點睇幾時維修？"},{"pid":"c7d659cca386b743e6717ddf38272a177e21614b","tid":120370,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"886c79bc35dfa1d0a28b53d8537c374e1b869294","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>油費好似好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n油價一定係等到400蚊樓下大量買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f06cb1db5039b0d8174c685f8eaa03d5e1062c","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點決定買二手機<br />\n同埋點睇幾時維修？</blockquote><br />\n二手機對新手來講係好好，<br />\n新玩我推薦爆買Dassault Mercury<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafb0b73ff42fdd129e91dbde95a29fef5944ec5","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點決定買二手機<br />\n同埋點睇幾時維修？</blockquote><br />\n二手機對新手來講係好好，<br />\n新玩我推薦爆買Dassault Mercury<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維修可以 Maintenance&gt;&gt;Plan new, 就會見到紅色格仔(距離維修時間) <br />\n另外有時飛機起飛壞左Repair 可以禁格來Repair 維修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意唔好禁Repair all, 會無左Realism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩問題可以係到問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329efcd204a1ff4ce22a3d6596194014c4b4222f","tid":120370,"uid":62038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:27:50.000Z","msg":"點可以改機票錢，買機番黎果陣 set得太高，而家冇人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2902f3c9460fc0050210d382f48ff772e21373cf","tid":120370,"uid":1731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"點解D機會突然少左人搭既?<br />\n對上一次都仲有98%人<br />\n然後今次得5%人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed45eb145fd78b1d672c77225bbaa0fff27f850e","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點可以改機票錢，買機番黎果陣 set得太高，而家冇人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係Flight 個頁簡想改條航線，入到去之後禁Route setting就得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bacc44de55d534dc51f7a27210a444ae4746b02","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解D機會突然少左人搭既?<br />\n對上一次都仲有98%人<br />\n然後今次得5%人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n温馨提示，當起飛超過20班機後就會成為認證航空公司，乘客量會根據需求定有大量改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n盡量簡番90%以上既地方飛同做個100% marketing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7e32d6d8d95ac7c63429cd60b7a7301f7037f1","tid":120370,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"隻GAME 整得麻麻地WO"},{"pid":"ee7deb530c7c062212812f8b530c024c58a1a5e6","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻GAME 整得麻麻地WO</blockquote><br />\n係呀，始終唔係主流既遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢本身係facebook game, 依家支援埋iOS同埋An<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係用黎燒下時間，慢慢一步一步睇住自己既機隊發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7728bbf84092e7ba7d96cd670c7f985d4767a8a","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:57:08.000Z","msg":"估唔到有巴打留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然人數唔多，我聽日得閒都整下教學分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要多啲香港人玩先好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2036d127c4bb64ad705e658fcefe59828cd5cc4d","tid":120370,"uid":9425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"20:00 FUEL PRICE : $350 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb466e4bc84877998f945d9380eb0ae6e446e91","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>20:00 FUEL PRICE : $350 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈佬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697e9e08360f5d58b6e742204a26b2fc51942183","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:31:24.000Z","msg":"Dear all<br />\n<br />\nThe route/aircraft limit has been increased from 375 to 400.<br />\n<br />\nThank you all for your patience and support <br />\n<br />\n翻譯：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各位<br />\n<br />\n機體及航線上限現已由375增加至400 <br />\n<br />\n多謝大家支持！</span><br />\n<br />\n呢條濕鳩 Developer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa346acc7624d537fab173b4b11856dfd829126","tid":120370,"uid":29864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"新手想問一開頭買咩二手機好？<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到樓上巴打講果隻Dassault Mercury <br />\n<br />\n搵Dassault 就有好多<br />\n<br />\n點揀d 二手機？距離愈遠愈好？<br />\n<br />\n同埋自己d 機係咪飛到幾遠就飛幾遠？"},{"pid":"bd4b11c33697dc23282f9708ec14d14e69c6feb5","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手想問一開頭買咩二手機好？<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到樓上巴打講果隻Dassault Mercury <br />\n<br />\n搵Dassault 就有好多<br />\n<br />\n點揀d 二手機？距離愈遠愈好？<br />\n<br />\n同埋自己d 機係咪飛到幾遠就飛幾遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDassault Mercure 係二手機到打 &quot;merc&quot; 就會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新玩主要搵短程＋客量高既機，Dassault Mercure 係首選 <br />\n飛到幾遠就飛幾遠&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; 正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n距離愈遠愈好？距離愈遠票價愈貴，但收成時間愈長，所以都係睇自己幾耐登入到一次"},{"pid":"a0ad1711daaada7adcd5ce6de9a4ea422a4bd2fc","tid":120370,"uid":29864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新手想問一開頭買咩二手機好？<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到樓上巴打講果隻Dassault Mercury <br />\n<br />\n搵Dassault 就有好多<br />\n<br />\n點揀d 二手機？距離愈遠愈好？<br />\n<br />\n同埋自己d 機係咪飛到幾遠就飛幾遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDassault Mercure 係二手機到打 &quot;merc&quot; 就會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新玩主要搵短程＋客量高既機，Dassault Mercure 係首選 <br />\n飛到幾遠就飛幾遠&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; 正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n距離愈遠愈好？距離愈遠票價愈貴，但收成時間愈長，所以都係睇自己幾耐登入到一次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係太常開到game 有無d 飛到7～8000 km 又戴客多既機推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db248ebfda0c5282de6fc1a2ba851f1d138570a","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新手想問一開頭買咩二手機好？<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到樓上巴打講果隻Dassault Mercury <br />\n<br />\n搵Dassault 就有好多<br />\n<br />\n點揀d 二手機？距離愈遠愈好？<br />\n<br />\n同埋自己d 機係咪飛到幾遠就飛幾遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDassault Mercure 係二手機到打 &quot;merc&quot; 就會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新玩主要搵短程＋客量高既機，Dassault Mercure 係首選 <br />\n飛到幾遠就飛幾遠&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; 正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n距離愈遠愈好？距離愈遠票價愈貴，但收成時間愈長，所以都係睇自己幾耐登入到一次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係太常開到game 有無d 飛到7～8000 km 又戴客多既機推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始選擇比較少，可以試下係高點收價既時候賣左一開始送既737, 買幾部 Dassault Mercure (一部最平40萬）可以係航線到加一個中轉站(Stopper) 黎增加航程長度同時間會最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好過買貴既長程二手機，客量少，Turnover慢，到你飛左20轉成為認證公司就會奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd458e333b6720cedafbfc11e158c16af35e414","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"小百科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/23/Air_Inter_Dassault_Mercure_at_Basle_-_February_1985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F2%2F23%2FAir_Inter_Dassault_Mercure_at_Basle_-_February_1985.jpg&h=31e4331f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n達梭水星(Dassault Mercure)是法國製的雙引擎噴射客機，於1967年設計，1973年首航，1995年退役。<br />\n<br />\n1967年，於法國政府支持下，達梭決定提出一個設計以與波音737競爭。其目標為此市場的高端部分－－相較於當時生產中的波音737隻有100座的737-100和115座的737-200，達梭將提出140座的噴射客機。從這架客機達梭可以在民航市場展示先前開發了許多種噴射戰鬥機所得到的知識，包括高速和低速空氣動力學升力。<br />\n達梭公司的創始人和老闆，Marcel Dassault，決定命名飛機為Mercure（法語「水星」之意）。「我想以神話中神祇的名字為這架飛機命名，只能找到一個神祇的頭盔和腳有翅膀，所以名為Mercure。」馬塞爾達梭說道。設計時使用了當時極為現代化的電腦。雖然體積比波音737大，但Mercure的速度卻較快。1969年6月在布爾歇機場的巴黎航展展示了全尺寸模型。1971年4月4日，原型機Mercure 01在達梭的Bordeaux-Merignac的工廠推出。其動力來自由兩個普惠JT8D-11（推力6，800公斤）。初次飛行是1971年5月28日，於M&eacute;rignac進行。第二架原型機裝置兩個普惠JT8D -15（也是後繼的同型機所使用的發動機），在1972年9月7日進行初次飛行。1973年7月19日，生產型首次飛行。1974年2月12日，Mercure得到了型號認證，1974年9月30日得到第IIIA類方法全天候自動着陸（最低能見度為500英尺，最低高度50英尺）的認證。Mercure 100還是第一架在飛行中全由女性飛行員駕駛的民航機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%81%94%E6%A2%AD%E6%B0%B4%E6%98%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%25A2%25AD%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%2598%259F&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7a77e27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%81%94%E6%A2%AD%E6%B0%B4%E6%98%9F</a>"},{"pid":"1d221d79c643908898b825b1edad7fe4032f9f77","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T18:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/11002ek.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F11002ek.jpg&h=72b872ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近開左條新航線接送港人同難民由香港經阿富汗到東京旅遊，幾乎班班爆滿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n航班編號: LX 110 <br />\n航班型號: Airbus A380-800<br />\n起飛地: 香港(啓德機場)-VHHX<br />\n經: 阿富汗(坎大哈國際機場)-OAKN<br />\n降落: 日本(羽田機場)-RJTT"},{"pid":"f1e5f60826842ad690b8dbecb67