gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570ffc020afff74d82f02a499d881c69fb8f444f","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/6b77a8a18c54f5ff1b13529292971ea8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F6b77a8a18c54f5ff1b13529292971ea8.png&h=22de8799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地今日黎講下上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAirline Manager 2 既上市係好濕鳩架，基本上係無咩用，唯一好玩既地方就係可以同 Game 內 PM 向你既全部投資者一次過發送大量垃圾資訊假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時有啲外國人會好熱情覆番你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新朋友由 Shares Sold 個到睇下有幾多股票俾人買左/入左股，我建議股價過左至少100先至Public(公開認購)，如果唔係有好多其他國家既新手會一下子買哂你全部股票，次後棄GAME，其他人就唔會買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n萬一唔好彩真係比新手買斷左你股份都唔洗驚，因為如果佢7日內唔上線，你可以申請回購股份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外你仲可以Publish Financial Report，等其他人評估下你間公司點樣（仲可以拎Achievement，會有Bonus Point送）<br />\n<br />\nPS：Bonus Point （BP） 係好難有，唔好亂用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每拎一個Achievement會送 5BP <br />\n每次收到Positive Article 會送 5BP<br />\n上Board討論區upvote/Downvote 人地既文，<br />\n每2000個會送200BP，總共1000BP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己BP用左黎：<br />\n1.開國際線 (50BP)<br />\n2.買牌照買原廠新機 (150BP)<br />\n3.買牌照買全新A380 (1500BP) <br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbe475660fab87c0bc830ec323b4e001fa31f03","tid":120370,"uid":35559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"岩岩4部機 depart, 係empty seat都係50%以上，係咪因為 0600早機關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n平時係坐爆咁滯"},{"pid":"1d335e08996cd48fa0bb2449dabf44b4816b5c41","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩4部機 depart, 係empty seat都係50%以上，係咪因為 0600早機關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n平時係坐爆咁滯</blockquote><br />\n巴打係咪剛剛玩起飛夠20班機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係既，就係因為你成為左認證玩家，你以後起飛既機都會受環境影響，<br />\n要開始睇Demand㨂航線, 同開始做Marketing增加人流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係既就睇番自己既Reputation(名氣)，有無做Marketing(要100%）<br />\n<br />\n另外早機唔會影響人流，因為我班班早機都好多難民同港豬塔(飛日本既)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91204789684c92c57b6d98233dccbeaf028a58f","tid":120370,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"呢隻好似真過另一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dd612c5e58b625116e062526c9241d85fa28c3","tid":120370,"uid":35559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩4部機 depart, 係empty seat都係50%以上，係咪因為 0600早機關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n平時係坐爆咁滯</blockquote><br />\n巴打係咪剛剛玩起飛夠20班機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係既，就係因為你成為左認證玩家，你以後起飛既機都會受環境影響，<br />\n要開始睇Demand㨂航線, 同開始做Marketing增加人流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係既就睇番自己既Reputation(名氣)，有無做Marketing(要100%）<br />\n<br />\n另外早機唔會影響人流，因為我班班早機都好多難民同港豬塔(飛日本既)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我啲機係飛泰國<br />\n睇過demand 99%<br />\nmarketing 96%"},{"pid":"5e23a1c4c724d947035bab22edebed806ad87df1","tid":120370,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻好似